➜泾河新城 向小康生活大踏步迈进——泾河新城全力推进脱贫攻坚工作扫描
http://www.sohu.com/a/425699132_100185418	14817
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201019/2ca23a1bd0a74a88852474318dee1fad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201019/2ac1c8b77ce94d99971d22ac69178763.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201019/18f1c7223bbd4184bfe5557a155125a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201019/ef86f399ee654ab2bc730cd162fef472.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
